OL,3,CJustice Secretary visits Southport
OL,4,Cmosque to show 'solidarity' after riots
OL,6,FThe Justice Secretary has praised the
OL,7,Fresponse to disorder over the summer
OL,8,Fas "the best of British" during a
OL,9,Fvisit to the Southport mosque that was
OL,10,Fbesieged by rioters.
OL,12,FShabana Mahmood met imam Ibrahim
OL,13,FHussein and other worshippers at the
OL,14,Fmosque, where she prayed before
OL,15,Fdiscussing their experience of the
OL,16,Fsummer's disorder.
