OL,3,CJustice Secretary visits Southport
OL,4,Cmosque to show 'solidarity' after riots
OL,6,FMr Hussein described being one of
OL,7,Fseven people trapped in the mosque
OL,8,Fwhile it was attacked by rioters
OL,9,Fthrowing missiles, telling the Justice
OL,10,FSecretary he had feared the building
OL,11,Fwould be burned down.
OL,13,FMs Mahmood said she had wanted to
OL,14,Fvisit the mosque soon after the
OL,15,Fattack, which came at the start of a
OL,16,Fweek of rioting that targeted Muslims
OL,17,Fand people from ethnic minorities.
