OL,3,CJustice Secretary visits Southport
OL,4,Cmosque to show 'solidarity' after riots
OL,6,FShe said: "This was my first
OL,7,Fopportunity to come and show
OL,8,Fsolidarity with the worshippers here
OL,9,Fafter everything they went through.
OL,11,F"But also to recognise the strength of
OL,12,Fcommunity spirit that saw off the
OL,13,Fforces of hate here in Southport and
OL,14,Facross the country as well, and to
OL,15,Fshow that we are always much stronger
OL,16,Fwhen we are united."
