OL,3,CJustice Secretary visits Southport
OL,4,Cmosque to show 'solidarity' after riots
OL,6,FThe Southport mosque was inundated
OL,7,Fwith offers of help following the
OL,8,Fattack, including a local bricklayer
OL,9,Fwho helped rebuild its wall, and
OL,10,Freceived cards from across the country
OL,11,Fexpressing support for them.
OL,13,FMs Mahmood said she was "deeply
OL,14,Fencouraged" by the response, comparing
OL,15,Fit to messages of support she had
OL,16,Freceived while facing "horrible weeks
OL,17,Fof intimidation and street-level
OL,18,Fharassment" during the general
OL,19,Felection.
