OL,3,CJustice Secretary visits Southport
OL,4,Cmosque to show 'solidarity' after riots
OL,6,FShe said: "I took such comfort from
OL,7,Feveryone who came out and, even if
OL,8,Fthey disagreed with the Labour Party
OL,9,For disagreed with me personally, was
OL,10,Fgiving me encouragement and support to
OL,11,Fkeep going, because they could see
OL,12,Fthat this was about our democratic
OL,13,Fvalues.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
