OL,3,CJustice Secretary visits Southport
OL,4,Cmosque to show 'solidarity' after riots
OL,6,F"And similarly, here talking to
OL,7,Fmembers of the mosque committee who
OL,8,Fwere here the night that they were all
OL,9,Fbeing attacked from the outside, and
OL,10,Fthere was a fire lit outside designed
OL,11,Fto set fire to this building, who were
OL,12,Fthen encouraged and given moral
OL,13,Fsupport by everybody else who turned
OL,14,Fup to help them out.
OL,16,F"It's a similar phenomenon, and I
OL,17,Fthink it's the best of British."
