OL,3,CJustice Secretary visits Southport
OL,4,Cmosque to show 'solidarity' after riots
OL,6,FMs Mahmood's visit came after the
OL,7,Fconclusion of the Labour Party
OL,8,Fconference in neighbouring Liverpool,
OL,9,Fat which the Prime Minister also
OL,10,Fpraised the response to the riots,
OL,11,Fwhile condemning the rioters as
OL,12,F"racist thugs".
